\" num=\"00008\">\n      <claim-text>8. The battery according to <claim-ref idref=\"CLM-00007\">claim 7</claim-ref>, wherein a weight ratio of the compound to the positive-electrode active material is 50% or more and 100% or less.</claim-text>\n    </claim>\n    <claim id=\"CLM-00009\" num=\"00009\">\n      <claim-text>9. The battery according to <claim-ref idref=\"CLM-00007\">claim 7</claim-ref>, wherein the negative electrode contains a negative-electrode active material that stores and releases lithium, and the electrolyte is a non-aqueous electrolyte solution.</claim-text>\n    </claim>\n    <claim id=\"CLM-00010\" num=\"00010\">\n      <claim-text>10. The battery according to <claim-ref idref=\"CLM-00007\">claim 7</claim-ref>, wherein the negative electrode contains a negative-electrode active material that stores and releases lithium, and the electrolyte is a solid electrolyte.</claim-text>\n    </claim>\n    <claim id=\"CLM-00011\" num=\"00011\">\n      <claim-text>11. The battery according to <claim-ref idref=\"CLM-00007\">claim 7</claim-ref>, wherein Me denotes one or more elements selected from the group consisting of Co, Ni, Fe, Al, Cu, Nb, Mo, Ti, Cr, Zr, Zn, Na, K, Ca, Mg, Pt, Au, Ru, and W.</claim-text>\n    </claim>\n  </claims>\n  ",
